{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b4/ee/111327_crt_YUoZ0.jpg?r=1718418041","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/b4/ee/111327_crt_YUoZ0.jpg?r=1718418041","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b4/ee/111327_crt_YUoZ0.jpg?r=1718418041","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b4/ee/111327_crt_YUoZ0.jpg?r=1718418041"},"name":"温水和彦","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/dd/dc/41073_prsn_ol77n.jpg?r=1633081644","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/dd/dc/41073_prsn_ol77n.jpg?r=1633081644","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/dd/dc/41073_prsn_ol77n.jpg?r=1633081644","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/dd/dc/41073_prsn_ol77n.jpg?r=1633081644"},"name":"梅田修一朗","short_summary":"梅田 修一朗（うめだ しゅういちろう、10月11日）は、日本の男性声優。千葉県出身。賢プロダクション所属。","career":["seiyu"],"id":41073,"type":2,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":111327},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/87/fc/111328_crt_KkuJo.jpg?r=1718462845","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/87/fc/111328_crt_KkuJo.jpg?r=1718462845","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/87/fc/111328_crt_KkuJo.jpg?r=1718462845","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/87/fc/111328_crt_KkuJo.jpg?r=1718462845"},"name":"八奈見杏菜","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264"},"name":"遠野ひかる","short_summary":"遠野 ひかる（とおの ひかる、1996年3月5日 - ）は、日本の女性声優。響所属。東京都出身。\r\n\r\nオーディションを経て、響の所属となった。同期には紡木吏佐がいる。‏\r\n初めて声をあてた作品はアプリゲーム『トリプルモンスターズ』のメリュジーナ･マーリン役である。\r\n\r\n特技\tダンス、栄養管理(家庭料理技能検定3級)\r\n趣味\t舞台鑑賞、ピアノ、読書","career":["seiyu"],"id":32639,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":111328},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/1